                     <interp inst="t18190217-81-off473" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190217-81-off473" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18190217-81-cd474" type="crimeDate">4th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190217-81-off473 t18190217-81-cd474"></join>, one scarf, value 10 s.; one pair of stockings, value 4 s. 6 d.; one pair of gloves, value 1 s.; one pair of shoes, value 2 s. 6 d.; one necklace, value 8 s.; one brooch, value 7 s.; one comb, value 6 d.; two pieces of net, value 8 s., and two yards of lace, value 11 s., the property of 
                     
